{"tid":568711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[期間限定] 中電筍工 日薪可達65萬","createTime":"2018-02-22T04:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T06:08:02.000Z","uid":42188,"like":5,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"49da4e028f8d765926a75ff9a0cf39a403a99bb7","tid":568711,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"紅磡機利士南路一個中電地盤昨日（10日）發生罕見奪命工業意外，3名工人身亡。中華電力有限公司今日發新聞稿指，中電股東會<span style=\"color: red;\">捐出150萬港元予3個家庭</span>，作子女教育及紓緩生活之用，另會<span style=\"color: red;\">向每個家庭發放15萬港元</span>慰問金作應急，並發起員工籌款。<br />\n<br />\n150萬/3 + 15萬 = 65萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa2f273a5613877d0847ed2007fedfa739cd47e","tid":568711,"uid":171816,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"On9當有趣"},{"pid":"aa2501071b895cada393d304da2b42916ad3d798","tid":568711,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T05:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440e47c4d3856050954829382e12edae5b898659","tid":568711,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"發發！"},{"pid":"00d7d3b4a3d8e2215118abd3330126ba3ea295d2","tid":568711,"uid":92603,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"祝福樓主新年行大運<br />\n<br />\n死完老豆死埋老母拎番幾十萬新年財"},{"pid":"98e47dc342878b6ff071206fbdbefeb72e6bbb3e","tid":568711,"uid":44678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"00d7d3b4a3d8e2215118abd3330126ba3ea295d2","tid":568711,"uid":92603,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"祝福樓主新年行大運<br />\n<br />\n死完老豆死埋老母拎番幾十萬新年財"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:04:27.000Z","msg":"比佢老豆老母拎啦，享下福<br />\n樓主死好啦"},{"pid":"44138e90201f81c2da01f30c8f8aa3c7793908c0","tid":568711,"uid":96743,"like":0,"